.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Temporary files
*.tmp
*.bak
*.txt
*#

# Anthropic files
AGENTS.md
CLAUDE.md
# Skills document the analysis API and are versioned alongside it. Git cannot
# re-include a child of an excluded directory, so .claude/ itself must be
# un-excluded (~/.gitignore_global excludes it) and only its contents ignored.
!.claude/
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/
*.local.md
*.mcp.json
.serena/
REVIEW.md

# Git worktrees
.worktrees/
